<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>By customizing your OpenCart shopping cart to streamline checkout‚Äîsuch as integrating multiple payment methods, simplifying form fields, and providing a guest checkout option‚Äîyou can significantly reduce these barriers. A smooth, user-friendly checkout process is crucial in minimizing cart abandonment and maximizing sales.&nbsp;</p>
